  - m_Id: 4761392354680832
    m_Localized: OK!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4761391968804864
    m_Localized: '{0} has checked this object'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5043163763826688
    m_Localized: '{0} poured the hot water onto Phil Ramen, mushed his noodles around
      and placed him on the table.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764210545287168
    m_Localized: OK!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764210641756160
    m_Localized: Nah
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764652905947136
    m_Localized: P-to-the-I-to-the-ZZA pockets
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764653417652224
    m_Localized: Looks just like the one I had as a kid
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764654109712384
    m_Localized: '*gulp* {0} feels HYDRATED.  Party HP and AP restored.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764654550114304
    m_Localized: It's out of service.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764654994710528
    m_Localized: Really wish Judge Judy were playing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764655435112448
    m_Localized: Sony Trinitron.  Nice.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764655871320064
    m_Localized: 'It says:  "Caution Sinkhole".  Weird, I don''t remember there being
      a hole here.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764656307527680
    m_Localized: Beer.  It's in you to give.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764656747929600
    m_Localized: Wait, what's this?!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764657192525824
    m_Localized: '{0} flipped the breaker.  An electrical humming  can be heard.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764657641316352
    m_Localized: Occupied!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764658081718272
    m_Localized: There's only one outlet and it's occupied by the busted microwave
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764658517925888
    m_Localized: Primton News - The latest beat, comin' to ya hunky snarky
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764658958327808
    m_Localized: Primton News - The latest beat, comin' to ya hunky snarky
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764659671359488
    m_Localized: It's {0}'s desk.  Do you want to save your progress?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764660367613952
    m_Localized: Judge Judy is playing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764660812210176
    m_Localized: Occupied!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764661252612096
    m_Localized: Nobody's home...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764661713985536
    m_Localized: Hello?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4765847351451648
    m_Localized: 'Maybe if I had something to pour this hot water into . . . '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764662611566592
    m_Localized: Still busted, they must have fired maintenance
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764663051968512
    m_Localized: Nobody's home...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764663504953344
    m_Localized: '{0} eats the warm ramen and recovers some AP.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764664066990080
    m_Localized: Hair is SIN
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4764664331231232
    m_Localized: It's {0}'s desk.  Do you want to save your progress?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4765847586332672
    m_Localized: It's an ad for a Sleep Mattress Canada.  (why buy a mattress anywhere
      else?)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4765847699578880
    m_Localized: It says "I bet you wish you knew what's behind this door."  Indeed,
      {0} does.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4765847800242176
    m_Localized: Frosty.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4765847900905472
    m_Localized: . . .
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4765847997374464
    m_Localized: Band posters in an office?  Cool.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766546927804416
    m_Localized: Can't go home yet, full day of work ahead
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5043164174868480
    m_Localized: 'Maybe if {0} had something to pour this hot water onto . . . '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766547263348736
    m_Localized: OK!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766547364012032
    m_Localized: Nah
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766547464675328
    m_Localized: 'It says:  Famous Zak''''s Tacos - CLOSED, due to vole infestation'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766547569532928
    m_Localized: 'There''s a note:  Please order from the window!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766547674390528
    m_Localized: Primm News - The latest beat, comin' to ya hunky snarky
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766547775053824
    m_Localized: 'There''s a note:  Not open!  Come back later!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766608105922560
    m_Localized: . . . no answer
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766608340803584
    m_Localized: '{0} hears loud music from inside.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766608449855488
    m_Localized: When pizza's on a bagel, you can eat pizza any time!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766608550518784
    m_Localized: '*Fluuuuuuush*  It must go the other direction south of the equator.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766608646987776
    m_Localized: Splish splash, I was takin' a bath
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766608747651072
    m_Localized: Ouch, it's pointy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766698086326272
    m_Localized: Nobody's home
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766876562350080
    m_Localized: Prim News - The latest beat, comin' to ya hunky snarky
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766876734316544
    m_Localized: 'Prim Luxury Homes:  "Live in the tallest building in Prim, why
      don''t''cha?"  - Prim Real Estate'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766876839174144
    m_Localized: Come visit the PortaBank! \nNow open in Prim South!  \n\n - this
      message brought to you by the Prim Infrastructure and Economic Development
      Committee
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766876944031744
    m_Localized: Don't jump!  \n\n  - this message brought to you by the Prim Mental
      Health and Sanctity of Life Committee
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766877044695040
    m_Localized: Authorized Personnel Only!  Trespassers will be prosecuted. - Prim
      Hydroelectric
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766877149552640
    m_Localized: 'There''s a note:  Please order from the window!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766877250215936
    m_Localized: 'There''s a note:  Not open!  Come back later!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766978743984128
    m_Localized: The elevator is out of service
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766978966282240
    m_Localized: The elevator is out of service
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766979079528448
    m_Localized: . . . {0} hears the sound of distant chattering
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766979180191744
    m_Localized: The elevator is out of service
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766979276660736
    m_Localized: . . . no answer
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766979377324032
    m_Localized: The elevator is out of service
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766979473793024
    m_Localized: . . . a fire alarm is chirping inside
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766979574456320
    m_Localized: The elevator is out of service
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766979670925312
    m_Localized: . . . {0} hears bossa nova playing gently through the door
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4766979771588608
    m_Localized: Congratulations!  You have reached the top of the tallest building
      in Prim.  Please enjoy this view.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767071324856320
    m_Localized: '{0} found a bumper car?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767127406895104
    m_Localized: Want a turkey leg?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767127612416000
    m_Localized: '{0} found a bumper car?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767217911586816
    m_Localized: 'Warning:  Dangerous wildlife ahead.  Maybe check out the Lacklustre
      Video first? \n  -signed People In Charge (PIC)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767218112913408
    m_Localized: Enjoy this vending machine! \n  -courtesy of Forest Modernization
      Team
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767218226159616
    m_Localized: No Entry due to Official Police Business Stuff. \n  -signed People
      In Charge (PIC)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767218331017216
    m_Localized: Your tax dollars at work!  Enjoy this tunnel! \n  -courtesy of Forest
      Modernization Team
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767218431680512
    m_Localized: Your tax dollars at work!  You asked, we listened!  This fallen
      tree slated to be removed in Winter 2014! \n  -courtesy of Forest Modernization
      Team
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767356197789696
    m_Localized: It looks like the workers here have scrawled a plan to take over
      the world.  It starts with . . . {0}'s eyes glaze over.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767356466225152
    m_Localized: No thanks!  I mean, I'm busy!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767356575277056
    m_Localized: It used to be really hard to breathe in here, so we added some fans
      ahead. \n  -courtesy of Tunnel Asthma Advocates
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767356675940352
    m_Localized: Frosty.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767785518358528
    m_Localized: Spawn Stuff?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767785702907904
    m_Localized: Spawn Stuff?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4767785807765504
    m_Localized: Spawn Stuff?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
